msgstr "중국어(간체) 우선"

#: engine/table.py:706
msgid "Switch to “Simplified Chinese before traditional”."
msgstr "“중국어(번체) 이전의 중국어(간체)로 전환”."

#. Translators: This is the menu entry to select when
#. one wants to input both Simplified and Traditional
